# Pages Directory

This directory contains page-level components for the six core pages:
- Dashboard: System overview and key metrics
- Projects: Project management and operations
- PullRequests: Code review and diff display
- Architecture: Architecture visualization and dependency analysis
- AnalysisQueue: Task queue management and scheduling
- Metrics: Metrics analysis and custom dashboards

Note: This is separate from the Next.js app directory and contains reusable page components.
